In this presentation, you will realize a juxtaposition between Agenda2030 and A.D. 31. During the time period when Christ was to be born and crucified, a few people within the Jewish nation and the surrounding nations were expecting and anticipating the coming of the Christ. Today, a few people are knowledgeable of Agenda2030 as a part of the Antichrist's satanic organization. The Bible states that before the second coming of Jesus Christ, the Antichrist will establish a tyrannical rule over the world.
